This manual supports the JB416 / JB419D / JB420 / JB424 / JB627 / JB632 models.

If you don't know what your model number is, use this simple technique. 

The JB represents the current design phase (gen 3 = 2006-....)

The first number represents how many cylinders you have.

The last 2 numbers represent the displacement. (ie. 2.0L = 20)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

IMPORTANT NOTES:
Generation 3 was released in 2006. The car had a facelift in 2009. 
This manual may not work for 2006-2008 vehicles.
2011 and later years only came with the J24 engines. (2.4L I-4)
2011 and later years DID NOT come with a 5-spd automatic.
